(i) We may occasionally use your name and email address to send you notifications regarding new services offered by TheHairStyler.com that we think you may find valuable.

If we wish to use your personal data for new purposes, we offer you the means to consent to those new purposes:

Disclosure and Visitor Choice We do not disclose your personal data to our subsidiaries or other organisations.
Confidentiality/Security We do not give visitors to our Web site the option of using a secure transmission method to send us their personal data.
We have implemented security policies, rules and technical measures to protect the personal data that we have under our control from:
unauthorised access improper use or disclosure unauthorised modification unlawful destruction or accidental loss
All our employees and data processors, who have access to, and are associated with the processing of personal data, are obliged to respect the confidentiality of our visitors' personal data.
We ensure that your personal data will not be disclosed to State institutions and authorities except if required by law or other regulation.
Access to the personal data we may hold about you You can ask us, by:
We do not provide our visitors with a readable copy of the personal data that we keep about them.
We do not allow our visitors to challenge the data that we hold about them.
We do reserve the right to refuse to provide you with a copy of your personal data.

We cannot demonstrate that our privacy policy accords with the privacy instrument.
Privacy Support If you have an enquiry or concern about our privacy policy, please contact:
Name/designation: Director, Public Relations Address: PO Box 808, Narellan - NSW, 2567 Email address: info@thehairstyler.com URL: https://www.thehairstyler.com
We do not recommend another means by which visitors' concerns may be addressed.

The Web site uses this information for the techincal administration of the web site, customer administration and marketing (email address).

The Web site uses this information, as well as information about phone/fax numbers and other, collected from public records and/or private organisations, for the technical administration of the web site, research and development, customer administration, marketing and trading in personal data.

Business Information The Web site uses information about an individual's employer, job, address, email, phone or other, collected from public records or private organisations, for the technical administration of the website, research and development, customer administration, marketing, and trading in personal data.
Other Personal Details and Profiling Data Individuals voluntarily supply their physical description and information about their lifestyle and personal tastes.
The Web site uses this information for the technical administration of the web site, customer administration and marketing.
